Introduction
==============

Vxkforum is clone of djangoBB app which aims to be 'I know everithing' application. 
I needed only forum functionality that can be easily integrated into existing
django site. I tried to strip the djangoBB down and wanted to push the changes to
original authors but found that original code is tightly coupled with the whole
functionality so I decided to rework it almost completely.

Installation
==============

1. Clone the read-only repo

     git clone git@github.com:vencax/django-vxk-forum.git

2. Install the dependencies via PIP.

     pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Add vxkforum into your INSTALLED_APPS as well as other dependant apps.

4. Include vxkforum.urls into your root url conf

     url(r'^forum/', include('vxkforum.urls', namespace='djangobb')),
     
NOTE: DO NOT FORGET to add the "namespace='djangobb'"
     
5. Add template conent processor and middleware in settings
		
		TEMPLATE_CONTEXT_PROCESSORS += (
			'vxkforum.context_processors.forum_settings',
		)
		
		MIDDLEWARE_CLASSES += (
			'vxkforum.middleware.LastLoginMiddleware',
		)
		
6. Add CKEditor configs into settings

		CKEDITOR_CONFIGS = {
		    'default': {
		        'toolbar': 'Full',
		        'toolbarCanCollapse': False,
		    },
		    'bbcode': {
		        'extraPlugins' : 'bbcode',
		        'toolbar': [
		            [      'Undo', 'Redo',
		              '-', 'Bold', 'Italic', 'Underline',
		              '-', 'Link', 'Unlink', 'Anchor',
		              '-', 'Format',
		              '-', 'SpellChecker', 'Scayt',
		              '-', 'Maximize',
		            ],
		            [      'HorizontalRule',
		              '-', 'Table',
		              '-', 'BulletedList', 'NumberedList',
		              '-', 'Cut','Copy','Paste','PasteText','PasteFromWord',
		              '-', 'SpecialChar', 'Blockquote',
		              '-', 'Image', 'Source',
		            ]
		        ],
		        'width': 900,
		        'toolbarCanCollapse': False,
		    }
		}
		
7. You are done


